msgid ""
"Fixed an issue where adding a control to a "
":class:`~qiskit.circuit.ControlledGate` with open controls would unset "
"the inner open controls. Fixes `#5857 <https://github.com/Qiskit/qiskit-"
"terra/issues/5857>`__"
