#: ../../release_notes.rst:3939
msgid ""
"The ``qiskit.execute`` module has been renamed to "
":mod:`qiskit.execute_function`. This was necessary to avoid a potentical "
"name conflict between the :func:`~qiskit.execute_function.execute` "
